ame will touch feeling of both boys and girls. Arcana and challenges are intertwined in a single story of the Happy Empire - A Bouquet for the Princess: Enhanced Edition game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More About the Game:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colorful graphics<br></li><li>Great emotions!!!<br></li><li>Game as part of a big story with rich storyline<br></li><li>4 amazing worlds to visit<br></li><li>64 unique, extended, captivating levels</li></ul><br>Help Princess Leya and Prince Hervald in their challenging journey and struggle for the Empire!",
